1. *Idete* li na posao? (Are you going to work?)
2. Oni su već *idoše* pre nekoliko minuta. (They had already gone a few minutes ago.)
3. Oni će *ići* u šetnju po parku. (They will go for a walk in the park.)
4. Ona nije *šla* na sastanak. (She didn't go to the meeting.)
5. Ja *idem* u školu. (I am going to school.)
6. Oni će *idi* u kino. (They will go to the movies.)